             was indicted for <rs id="t18030420-7-off31" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18030420-7-off31" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18030420-7-off31" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18030420-7-cd32" type="crimeDate">24th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18030420-7-off31 t18030420-7-cd32"></join>, a watch, value 5l. another watch, value 30s. a gold key; value 5s. a metal watch-chain, value 2d. two gold seals, value 21s. two gold lockets, value 30s. three china dishes, value 5s. a tea-chest, value 10s. a china tureen, value 12s. a pair of breeches, value 10s. eight silver table-spoons, value 4l. 11s. a silver gravy-spoon, value 30s. fifteen silver tea-spoons, value 35s. and a pair of silver tea-tongs, value 12s. the property of 
                     <persName id="t18030420-7-victim105" type="victimName">
                        John 
                        Sanders
                     <interp inst="t18030420-7-victim105" type="surname" value="Sanders"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18030420-7-victim105" type="given" value="John"></interp>
